                        .content 
                            .blurb
                                h1 GitNotes (Beta)

                                p As developers we love #[span version control] tools.  #[span Github] has been a foundation for sharing ideas that both help the developer control their workflow and encourage community input.

                                p Why does a tool as great as Github only serve people that can code?

                                p GitNotes is a callaborative project with local Austin writers to attempt to abstract out the concepts of version control; such as  branching, pull requests, and commits. This site is built using  JQuery's .ajax() method and the  Github API v3.

